cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is primarily focused on attacking video recognition models, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The use of reinforcement learning (RL) also suggests that it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, since the experiments are conducted on public datasets, it could also be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, since the paper deals with adversarial attacks, it could also be categorized under cryptography and security (cs.CR).
